Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:46.51,zw,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.23,0:21:48.37,zw,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.72,0:21:50.57,zw,NTP,0,0,0,,明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.89,0:23:34.73,zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如今我仍旧在这里守望着
